I thought it would be empowering to women to see them rally after being misused, instead they fought with each other the whole time trying to get this strange man to bed them. Is that really how people are? A guy shows up, everyone says they want nothing to do with him, then they break old friendships over petty jealousy? Knowing that he tries to woo all of them (from the trailer) made all of his actions in the movie seem really creepy and not romantic at all.
